
2 DIRECTIONS->VERTICAL AND HORIZONTAL

1.VERTICAL->row form means main axis
2.HORIZONTAL->column form means cross axis

flex basis->sets up the height or width

sample code

   .container {
      color: white;
      border: 5px solid gold;
      display: inline-flex;
      flex-direction: column;
   
    }
    .container div{
      flex-basis: 100px;
    }
